isit: <a href=\"https://teespring.com/ros-kinectic-kame\">https://teespring.com/ros-kinectic-kame</a> and <a href=\"https://teespring.com/ros-kinetic-kame-eu\">https://teespring.com/ros-kinetic-kame-eu</a> directly.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.8px;\">\r\n</span></span>\r\n<div><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px;\"></span></div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div class=\"asset-footer\"></div>\r\nIf you\'d like us to spotlight your project here, send us a note at info AT osrfoundation DOT org.\r\n<a href=\"http://www.ros.org/news/spotlight/\" target=\"_blank\">Previous spotlights</a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','ROS Spotlight','','inherit','closed','closed','','268-revision-v1','','','2016-04-18 18:40:03','2016-04-18 18:40:03','',268,'http://www.ros.org/268-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0);
